<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML+RDFa 1.0//EN" "http://www.w3.org/MarkUp/DTD/xhtml-rdfa-1.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
      xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
      xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
      xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
      metal:use-macro="context/@@engine/macros/page"
      i18n:domain="cc_org">
<head>
  <title metal:fill-slot="title">Choose a License</title>
</head>
<body>


  <metal:title metal:fill-slot="page-header-title"
	       i18n:translate="license.here_chosen">
    Here is the license you've chosen
  </metal:title>

<div metal:fill-slot="body"
      tal:define="target_lang string:en;">

<div class="licensebox">
<div tal:omit-tag="" i18n:translate="license.selected">
<span tal:omit-tag="" i18n:name="license_url" tal:content="view/license/uri" />
<span tal:omit-tag="" i18n:name="country_name" tal:content="python: '' " />
You have selected the <span i18n:name="license_pretty_name" tal:replace="python: view.license.name" />.  <a href="#" tal:attributes="href view/license/uri">See how the license will look</a> to your site's visitors.
</div>

<div style="margin-top:10px; text-align:center;">
<table tal:attributes="dir view/get_ltr_rtl;"><tr>
<td style="text-align:center">
<a tal:attributes="href view/license/uri"
   href="#"><img id="licensebutton" alt="Creative Commons License" tal:attributes="src view/license/imageurl" src="" style="margin-right:10px;margin-bottom:4px; border: 0;" /></a>
<br/><input type="radio" name="button" checked="checked" onclick="" tal:attributes="onclick python: 'swapbutton(\''+view.license.imageurl+'\')'"/>
</td>
<td style="text-align:center">
<a tal:attributes="href view/license/uri"
   href="#"><img id="licensebutton_some" alt="Creative Commons License" src="http://creativecommons.org/images/public/somerights20.png" style="margin-right:10px;margin-bottom:4px;" /></a>
<br/><input type="radio" name="button" onclick="swapbutton('http://creativecommons.org/images/public/somerights20.png')"/>
</td>
<td style="text-align:center" valign="bottom" tal:condition="not:request/wiki|nothing">
<a tal:attributes="href view/license/uri"
   href="#"><img id="licensebutton_slim" alt="Creative Commons License" tal:attributes="src view/license/slim_image" src="" style="margin-right:10px;margin-bottom:4px; border: 0;" /></a>
<br/><input type="radio" name="button" onclick="" tal:attributes="onclick python: 'swapbutton(\''+view.license.slim_image+'\')'"/>
</td>
</tr></table>
</div>
</div>

<h2 style="margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:8px;" i18n:translate="license.what_to_do_next">What to do next</h2>

<div style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:30px;">
	<h4 i18n:translate="license.have_your_own_website">Have your own website?</h4>

	<p i18n:translate="license.copy_text">Copy the text below to your Web site to let your visitors know what license applies to your works.</p>

	<form action="">
    <div>
	    <textarea id="codetocopy" name="html" style="width:90%;height:150px;" rows="8" cols="20" tal:content="structure view/license/escapehtml"/>
    </div>
	</form>


<p i18n:translate="license.select_text">
<span tal:content="request/QUERY_STRING" 
      tal:omit-tag=""
      i18n:name="url_vars" >
Select the contents of the box above and copy it. Or, have it <a href="/license/work-html-popup?lang=en&amp;license_code=by-nc-nd&amp;title=efwefewf" onclick="window.open('http://creativecommons.org/license/work-html-popup?lang=en&amp;license_code=by-nc-nd&amp;title=efwefewf', 'html_help', 'width=400,height=350,scrollbars=yes,resizable=yes,toolbar=no,directories=no,location=yes,menubar=no,status=yes');return false;">emailed to yourself.</a>
</span>
</p>

<p><strong i18n:translate="license.read_tutorial">Need more help? <a href="http://creativecommons.org/education/publish-website">Read our tutorial</a>.</strong></p>

<p i18n:translate="license.after_support_cc">After publishing your license, please consider <a href="http://creativecommons.org/support/">supporting Creative Commons</a>.</p>
	
</div>


		
<!-- <div metal:use-macro="here/license_macros/macros/languages">
  language box
</div>
-->

</div>

<metal:sidebar fill-slot="sidebar">
<h4 i18n:translate="license.no_web_site">No Web site?</h4>

<p i18n:translate="license.learn_host">Learn about other places you can host your licensed files. These
sites work with your Creative Commons license.</p>

<ul>
	<li><a href="http://creativecommons.org/audio/publish-internetarchive" 
	       i18n:translate="license.publish_audio_ia"
	       class="publish-links">Publishing your licensed music to the Internet Archive</a></li>
	<li><a href="http://creativecommons.org/audio/publish-soundclick" 
	       i18n:translate="license.publish_soundclick"
	       class="publish-links">Publishing your licensed music to Soundclick</a></li>

	<li><a href="http://creativecommons.org/image/publish-flickr" 
	       i18n:translate="license.publish_flickr"
	       class="publish-links">Posting your licensed images at Flickr</a></li>
	<li><a href="http://creativecommons.org/image/publish-buzznet" 
	       i18n:translate="license.publish_buzznet"
	       class="publish-links">Posting your licensed images at Buzznet</a></li>	
	<li><a href="http://creativecommons.org/text/publish-weblogs" 
	       i18n:translate="license.publish_blog"
	       class="publish-links">Adding a Creative Commons license to your blog (Blogger, Movable Type, and Typepad)</a></li>	
	<li><a href="http://creativecommons.org/video/publish-internetarchive" 
	       i18n:translate="license.publish_video_ia"
	       class="publish-links">Publishing your licensed video at the Internet Archive</a></li>
	 <li><a href="/audio/publish-morpheus" 
	       i18n:translate="license.publish_morpheus"
	       class="publish-links">Publishing your licensed music to the Morpheus P2P network</a></li>
       <li i18n:translate="license.mark_xmp">
	<%=[ccommons::istr $lang license.mark_xmp]%>
	<span tal:omit-tag="" i18n:name="url_vars" 
	      tal:content="request/QUERY_STRING" />
	</li>
       <li i18n:translate="license.mark_nonweb">
	<%=[ccommons::istr $lang license.mark_nonweb]%>	
	<span tal:omit-tag="" i18n:name="url_vars" 
	      tal:content="request/QUERY_STRING" />
	</li>
</ul>	
</metal:sidebar>

</body>
</html>
